snippet.title: Measurement - Finding Area & Perimeter of a Rectangle Using Mushrooms
snippet.description: http://tapintoteenminds.com In order to add context to finding area and perimeter, we will use a mushroom container and measure in mushrooms.  Great for making math contextual, visual and interconnected.
